document_data.Description:
{{quote
|Know I anything of that loyal man, 'tis this: alive or dead, he'll be at his post.
|An adventurer.
}}
Baldassar was a loyal guard captain that fought with a blue [[shield]] and a [[longsword]]. He had light brown hair and a large moustache. He wore a grey-brown [[leather armor|leather jerkin]] with brown [[trousers]], boots and a mantle.
